snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3741 - Babita Wins a Car?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey

Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka

snippet.description:
#WhereIsPushpa #Pushpa2TheRule #AlluArjun

Where is Pushpa? Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Hindi Glimpse !!!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings,  the film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Suneel, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing were performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Karthika Srinivas respectively.

snippet.title: FAMILY AUR SHAADI KI SHOPPING..!!
snippet.description:
Let's take you men's wear shopping for the festive wedding season at the most happening place in Hyderabad in the Banjara Hills at the Asuka Store

Walk in and experience the medley of heritage and old world charm with the modern, just like their collection, and exult in the ritual of fine dressing, an experience that's gonna leave you savouring in the fragrance of tommorow!

The design house hails from Delhi where they've been manufacturers of men's wear garments for over 35 years. From ceremonial suits for festive occasions, Sherwanis for Weddings, ornate Bandhgalas, Kurtas, indowestern attire in wide range of hues, fabrics, embroidery, and matching shoes and accesories, it's a one stop shop for men who like to dress the best! 

Shop Ethnic and Western Men's wear at Asuka Store 
Visit : Banjara Hills, Road No. 2, Hyderabad

Instagram : @ asukacouture

For Business Inquiry : hyderabaddiaries@yahoo.com

Second Channel:
Hyderabad Diaries Vlogs: www.youtube.com/hyderabaddiariesvlogs

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3741 - 10 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3741: Popatlal Wins The Honeymoon Coupon
--------------------------------------------------------
Residents of Gokuldham are impatiently awaiting the announcement of the winner. The announcement of the final two coupon rewards has all of the society's members prepared. Popatlal jumps excitedly as he wins the honeymoon package in his coupon and gets to know that he can avail the prize within a year. The winner is announced by the company as Taarak and Babita get the same starting serial number. Who will take home the car in this jackpot? To find out, watch the episode!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3741, 10 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

नर्मदा किनारे रेत पर दौड़ती ज्योतिबाई रघुवंशी का वीडियो वायरल,
बीते एक सप्ताह से शहपुरा से जबलपुर के बीच नर्मदा किनारे घूम रही हैं ज्योति बाई,
आस्था या अंधविश्वास,
ज्योतिबाई के दर्शन करने उमड़ रही हजारों लोगों की भीड़,
नर्मदापुरम पिपरिया में दर्ज है ज्योतिबाई की गुमशुदगी,
नर्मदा की बेटी मानकर ज्योतिबाई के पीछे घूम रहे हजारों लोग.

#viral #narmada #miracle #omg #narmadaparikrama #jabalpur #mpnews

snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Part 1 ft. Benafsha Soonawalla | Music Prod By @BluishMusic & Sez On The beat
snippet.description:
Boyfriend is a song where Dino James portrays the insecurities and toxicity that an individual can go through in a relationship and the trauma that follows if they let themselves fall deep into the dark hole of insecurities. An uncomfortable truth that a lot of people face. Through this song, Dino James has a strong message, “If this is what people face, best for both parties to walk away. Toxicity and trauma is never okay”.

snippet.title: బెంగుళూరు స్పెషల్ అద్భుతమైన కారా బాత్ నీరు చట్నీ | Hotel Style Kara Bath with Neer Chutney Recipe
snippet.description:
బెంగళూర్ స్పెషల్ అద్భుతమైన కారా బాత్ నీరు చట్నీ | Hotel Style Kara bath with Neer Chutney in telugu | Bangalore Special Breakfast Kara Bath Neer Chutney

Hello Foodies!
In this video, we'll show you how to make a delicious and spicy Bangalore special Kara Bath recipe, along with a Neer Chutney that perfectly complements the dish. Kara Bath is a popular breakfast dish in Bangalore, made with semolina, vegetables, and a blend of aromatic spices. We'll show you how to make this flavorful dish step-by-step and also share some tips and tricks to make it even more delicious. And to balance out the spiciness of the Kara Bath, we'll also be making a simple and spicy Neer Chutney, made with coconut, green chilies, and coriander. This chutney is the perfect accompaniment to the Kara Bath and will leave you feeling satisfied. So, follow the steps shown in this video to learn how to make this classic Bangalore breakfast dish with a twist!

బెంగళూర్ స్పెషల్ అద్భుతమైన కారా బాత్ నీరు చట్నీ | Hotel Style Kara bath with Neer Chutney in telugu | Bangalore Special Breakfast Kara Bath Neer Chutney

Hello Foodies!
In this video, we'll show you how to make a delicious and spicy Bangalore special Kara Bath recipe, along with a Neer Chutney that perfectly complements the dish. Kara Bath is a popular breakfast dish in Bangalore, made with semolina, vegetables, and a blend of aromatic spices. We'll show you how to make this flavorful dish step-by-step and also share some tips and tricks to make it even more delicious. And to balance out the spiciness of the Kara Bath, we'll also be making a simple and spicy Neer Chutney, made with coconut, green chilies, and coriander. This chutney is the perfect accompaniment to the Kara Bath and will leave you feeling satisfied. So, follow the steps shown in this video to learn how to make this classic Bangalore breakfast dish with a twist!

snippet.title: POORI | King Of Poori Recipe | Wheat Poori Recipe Cooking in Village | Crispy Fluffy Puri Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a large quantity of wheat poori recipe. We use only wheat flour and cold pressed gingelly oil to make this poori recipe healthy and traditional.

Finally, we enjoy the puri recipe with our favorite mutton curry!

The taste is, Crispy and Yummy!

snippet.title: UNVEILING MY FIRST SUPERCAR !!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the thrilling journey of my first supercar reveal! It has been a long and exciting road to get to this point, and I am beyond thrilled to share it with all of you.

From the initial concept sketches to the countless hours of testing and refining, every step of this journey has been a labor of love. And now, finally, the moment has arrived to unveil this beauty to the world.

This journey has been a wild ride, but I couldn't be more proud of the final result. So come along with me and let's experience the excitement and awe of the first supercar reveal together!

snippet.description:
Gangulu Full Song | Ft. Maanas, Vishnu Priya | Bheems Ceciroleo | New Telugu Folk Songs 2023

Get ready to unleash your inner fire with Vishnu Priya and Maanas' electrifying new release "Gangulu"! This song is an explosive blend of high-energy beats, pulsating rhythms, and raw, unbridled passion that is guaranteed to get your heart racing and your body moving.

After "Zari Zari", the hit pair is back to take the stage by storm with their explosive dance performance in Gangulu song.

Farq Episode 47 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 10th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
aarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Episode 66 | Turkish Drama | Urdu Dubbing | SenCal Kapimi | 9th April 2023 |
snippet.description:
Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Sen Cal Kapimi | You knock on my Door |


#Urdu1 #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed #sencalkapimi #sençalkapımı #DastakMayrayDilPay #sençalkapımı #sencalkapimi #youknockonmydoor #handeercel #handeerçel #kerembürsin #karembursin #melisadöngel #bigeönal #loveisintheair #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

Farq Episode 48 Teaser - 10th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3740 - 8 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3740: Lucky Draw Ka Din
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal warns that he would take severe action against Ramsang Corporation if no one from Gokuldham wins the prize. Popatlal is notified by Jetha that Ramsang is among the most well-known businesses in the industry and that they will not put up with such unfounded accusations. Before the lucky draw is broadcasted, Bhide makes the request that everyone observe decorum and silence so that everyone can watch the program in peace. Finally, the lucky draw starts and everyone starts staring at the television in awe. Residents of Gokuldham are impatiently awaiting the announcement of the winner. Who will take home the car in this jackpot? To find out, watch the episode!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3740, 8 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Legacy - Amit Bhadana (Official Music Video) | Bintu Pabra | KP Kundu | The Kidd | Vaksh Vimal |
snippet.description:
This song is the fourth single by Amit Bhadana. After Parichay, Aatmvishvas and Father Saab now i bring you Legacy. Through Legacy I am trying to convey a simple message - If you choose not to be the part of the rat race, stay firm on your resolve and never compromise on your principles you can achieve anything under the sun. This song showcase Three major chunks of My life, one in my village where 5 years of my life were spent, second where i spent 20 years in Delhi and my present life where i am fullfilling all my dreams and taking care of my family .You will get a glimpse of my journey from village to city, days of extreme poverty in a new location and my struggle. With hardwork i overcame every hardship and created a better life for myself and my loved ones. I believe that this is just the beginning. I dream of a much better future and need every bit of your support to make it a reality. With quality content, creativity and vision I want to add value to my viewers lives. In the past 6 years I have learnt alot and taught alot (you know it better) and I wish to keep entertaining everyone for the rest of my life. I want to create a legacy that goes on from genaration to generation Please watch this song and don’t forget to share it with your family and friends. Legacy. Love.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Qalandar Episode 55 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - 9th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl’s firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn’t complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz’s parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz’s life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz’s half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

Head of Project: Mikaal Zulfiqar
Written By: Samra Bukhari
Directed By: Saima Waseem

snippet.title: नया चेहरा, नई पहचान | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 678
snippet.description:
नया चेहरा, नई पहचान | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 678

After an unfortunate event, Thapki undergoes plastic surgery. She recovers fully, but the Pandeys are shocked to see her. She looks completely different! Aryan, however, refuses to believe that it's Thapki. Is Aryan's intuition true? 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. snippet.title: Taakat - Seedhe Maut x DJ Sa ft. Lil Bhavi
snippet.description:
Streaming Link: https://lnk.to/Taakat
Lyrics - 

Encore

Mai aata vaha se jaha pe bache baithe mu fulake
Kyuki ye teacher bina baat ke mar raha hai chaante
To bunk hai classein ghar pe gai khabar to 
Toote gaand hai
Par dum hai gaand me
Inke dollo se bade yaha aand hai 
Andar se nazuk chamdi moti dil se malamaal hai
Mukesh ko kehdo ke hum naii sadi ke shaktimaan hai

Bachpan se bas ek hi plan hai
Sab bado ki lenge kehke
 Apne mann ki sabse pehele

Hook
Tu kare jaae aalas, ghaatak aadat
“Mai raha nahi balak “ wala  hai ye mijaz sab Aadar kare hum pen se bimar 
Hai taaqat
Hai taqat , lagat ,shauhrat , ainth aur aafat 
Maal aur kavita , benz aur profit
Pyar aur parivar sang
Aur saath me sa aur sare aam road pe moshpit

Encore 

Hotshit, hii power socket
Kaha gaya dhyaan mera shit i lost it
Khada hu mai chaand pe i may jump off it
Chud chuki maa mere in kandho ki 
Chid chuki gaand tab bhi  inn bando ki 
Chadh rahi jhaanjh hai ab in bhasdo ki 
To rahi nahi maansik hai  in bacho si
Kare yaha na bhool ke bhi  koi bakchodi

Calm

Wo chahte bano doctor uh
Jab chota tha me banna tha bas kakarot 
Trauma leke badhe hote bande bohot 
Role model tha bas hip hop 
Dost gaya jail 10 saal kam se kam 
Koi bola ek life hai don’t fuck this up 
Usne sune bas aakhri teen shabd 
 Hai karam iss gaane ka sheershak 
Par koi maange maafi likhit to likhunga deez nuts
Shiv naresh ki t shirt se 
dosto me tees take ki deal tak 
Abj me offico me dere the interview 
Uss same bees rupe bhi the bohot 
Body count uss same bhi tha galt 
Banna ni ek raat me badha sa cult
Nalle baatein kare jaayein
Gaane baje jayein 
muh kara sabka band

Tu kare jaae aalas, ghaatak aadat
“Mai raha nahi balak “ wala  hai ye mijaz sab Aadar kare hum pen se bimar 
Hai taaqat
Hai taqat , lagat ,shauhrat , ainth aur aafat 
Maal aur kavita , benz aur profit
Pyar aur parivar sang
Aur saath me sa aur sare aam road pe moshpit

Lil Bhavi 

Ab chamach nhi cup mai hai syrup
Colony mai pudiya vo  business 
Bawe mai dagger  tu scissor 
Jo sunra colony vo real

Mai fsta ni bsdo mai kabil 
Unhe. bolu  ni sir  jo hai staaf se 
Meri tutan ye chalu hai raat din
Bnde kr chuke  scene ab vo bawe Harsamay rhesmay 

Bani thoot ki. Chut fooke ghaas ye vesheli
Bnde 420 bnde phoche kacheri 
Bawe  lenge cheen meri sathi maaddy 
Mere haath mai lean  or usmai hai candy
Hum deete ghaaw  chle haato mai chabi 
Hum nikle fast  jb ayi villo ki gaadi 
Mai dera trap mera kaam na saarkari
Ye chaapad gang   Hur muudo mai shamil
Hrsmay 

Cap none nayi hai dilli ye seven one 
Trap meri shit  karu rap kum
Kachra bhavi vo hai past tense
Lube mujhai chaheye naa vaseline
Mudda uchaala fir cash in
Dilli mai kachre hai manyy
Dekhu mai badte gye enemy

Tu kare jaae aalas, ghaatak aadat
“Mai raha nahi balak “ wala  hai ye mijaz sab Aadar kare hum pen se bimar 
Hai taaqat
Hai taqat , lagat ,shauhrat , ainth aur aafat
